<br>
Since I have no intention of farming until I can afford most of them, I'm looking for advice on which spells are the most beneficial as I move from 8 on up. Should I concentrate on better fire power, personal shielding, etc?  Or should I concentrate on pet-related spells for better tanks?<br>
<br>
One other question. Where can I buy malachite? I found one vendor in Kelethin (outside the jewelry shop) that had some for a while, but the last few times I've gone there, she hasn't had any. I haven't found any in Felewithe, but then I haven't checked them all either. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227428">Kuldar</a><br>
Druzzil Ro</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uscrubfire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>scrubfire</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 159<br> <font color=#333333>(7/8/02 4:39:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1394.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Which level 8 spells should I buy?</span><hr size=1> Buy at least one of your level 8 pets first.  From levels 4 to 12, my favorite pet was the water pet. <p>--------------------------<BR>
